- Focus detail on the most recent and relevant roles. Use fewer bullets for older or less relevant work.
- Best bullet formula: action verb + what was built, improved, or delivered + tools or context + result
- Use metrics when supported, especially in recent roles, but do not force fake numbers or unrealistic density
